-- Monsanto drops after broker downgrade
-- 
-- Thu Oct 2, 2008 8:19am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/02/us-markets-stocks-monsanto-idUSTRE4913Z520081002

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Monsanto Co ( MON.N ) fell more than 6 percent to $91.40 before the bell on Thursday after Merrill Lynch slashed its recommendation on the biotech seed company's stock to "neutral" from "buy." 

 (Reporting by  Ellis Mnyandu ; Editing by Theodore d'Afflisio)